# Trade with Tayyab — Frontend Environment Configuration
#
# The frontend calls the backend using relative /api/... paths, which are
# rewritten to the backend by vercel.json (production) and by the dev proxy
# in vite.config.ts (local). You normally do NOT need to set anything here.
#
# Only set VITE_API_URL if you change the code to read an absolute base URL.
# VITE_API_URL=https://trade-with-tayyab-lms.onrender.com
